{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8ecc69d4b9","title":"关于大批判的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4d82aa1c1b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"8ecc69d4b9","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2aa352c18c","type":"title","text":"关于大批判的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"8ecc69d4b9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8787cd536d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、批判要踏实，要调查确实，不然会一风吹。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"8ecc69d4b9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8c802c182a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、文章要一、二千字，短一点，写一个问题。一个问题说明了就行了。不能超过三千字，长了没人看，看了也记不清。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"8ecc69d4b9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c6350b8d2","type":"paragraph","text":"三、驯服工具论要批判，但也要有无产阶级纪律，服从、团结都是有条件的。四、托拉斯不能都推翻吧？旧名词可以有新内容，主要批判他走资本主义道路。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"8ecc69d4b9","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":573,"end":573}}}},"__N_SSG":true}